<li class='cover' id='bookCover_55120318'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/55120318-stories-of-hope"><img alt="Stories of Hope: Finding Inspiration in Everyday Lives" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1598367517l/55120318._SY160_.jpg" />
